<strong>Application Layer</strong><br>
The application layer includes a utility for data abstraction, algorithm catalog, and suite of visualizations all from a simple user interface or API/SDK.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Algorithm Catalog</strong>
<br>
The algorithm catalog enables users to discover or create new algorithms.  Each algorithm in the catalog is tagged with meta data for search and discovery.   Detailed descriptions explain how and when to use the algorithm.  Algorithm developers can create or upload new algorithms in the catalog for use by others.  The catalog sits on top of the Algorithms.io data infrastructure so algorithms can be deployed against data on the system.  All of this happens in the cloud so there are no downloads or complex code packages to deal with. It's never been easier to get more value of your data.
<br>
