        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-body collapse">
            <div class="accordion-inner">
The runtime environment is built on a patent pending workflow system that enables algorithms to be chained together.  It allows both parallel and non parallel algorithms in multiple programming languages to be sequentially combined for the creation of complex algorithmic workflows.  These workflows can be run against data sets or streams to produce meaningful results or new data products. The runtime environment has native support for big data jobs on Hadoop and supports asynchronous and synchronous calls to provide results depending on your needs.
